The Wolf of Wall Street;;83;;79;;R;;In 1987, Jordan Belfort (Leonardo DiCaprio) takes an entry-level job at a Wall Street brokerage firm. By the early 1990s, while still in his 20s, Belfort founds his own firm, Stratton Oakmont. Together with his trusted lieutenant (Jonah Hill) and a merry band of brokers, Belfort makes a huge fortune by defrauding wealthy investors out of millions. However, while Belfort and his cronies partake in a hedonistic brew of sex, drugs and thrills, the SEC and the FBI close in on his empire of excess.;;Biography,Comedy,Drama;;Martin Scorsese;;2013;;Leonardo DiCaprio,Jonah Hill,Margot Robbie,Matthew McConaughey,Kyle Chandler,Jon Bernthal,Jon Favreau,Rob Reiner,Jean Dujardin,Joanna Lumley,Cristin Milioti,Christine Ebersole,Shea Whigham,Katarina Cas,P.J. Byrne,Kenneth Choi,Brian Sacca,Henry Zebrowski,Ethan Suplee;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_wolf_of_wall_street_2013